holidayRental.headline: BEACH BLUE
holidayRental.description:
With captivating ocean views from almost every room, this property offers guests the ultimate coastal experience. Accommodating a maximum of 12 guests, this large 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located within walking distance of the beach and shops. Features fully equipped kitchen with dishwasher, two lounge areas, balcony with outdoor setting, barbecue, and a cosy indoor fireplace for the winter months. Includes 3 Queen beds, 1 Double bed and 1 Bunk bed.

Linen is not included but can be provided on request at an additional cost of $50 per night or $220 per week. If you would like linen included for your stay please advise at the time of the booking so that the correct price can be calculated. Please note an additional $40 booking fee applies to all bookings and a $1,000 security bond holding is required for this property. Minimum stay is 2 nights over the weekend or 3 nights midweek. All bookings during the Christmas School Holidays are in 7 night blocks from Monday to Monday. No pets allowed.
